title: Dinner at the Creek
description: Bernard is left in charge for the evening, so Craig sets out to find his own dinner at the creek.

title: Hyde & Zeke
description: Craig and his friends are challenged to find the greatest hider that Hide and Seek has ever known.

title: Silver Fist Returns
description: There's a thief in the Creek, and there is only one hero who can stop them: SILVER FIST!

title: Turning the Tables
description: Craig dines at the restaurant where his older brother works and orders up a plate of REVENGE... and lots of breadsticks.

title: Sleepover at JP's
description: JP invites his friends over for a sleepover, but it happens to be on the night of a huge game of Flashlight Tag in the Creek!

title: Craig and the Kid's Table
description: It's a Williams Family Thanksgiving, which means it's time to reunite The Kid's Table! But when Bernard accidentally destroys dessert, Craig uses the power of the Kids Table to help save his brother from certain grounding.

title: The Haunted Dollhouse
description: Craig and his friends find themselves being followed by a creepy doll and its haunted dollhouse.

title: The Anniversary Box
description: Craig is entrusted with a special anniversary gift for his mom, and immediately loses it in the Creek.

title: My Stare Lady
description: Craig enters a dangerous staring contest, hoping to win another one of Kenneth's Cubes.

title: Escape from Family Dinner
description: There's a huge water balloon fight at the creek but Craig is stuck at home for a family dinner, unless he can escape.

title: The Takeout Mission
description: Kelsey leads her friends on the most important quest ever, picking up takeout for dinner.

title: Creek Talent Extravaganza
description: Hoping to help the Creek Daycare, Craig organizes a talent show.

title: Scoutguest
description: Craig finds himself with an unlikely house guest when Jason the Junior Forest Scout sleeps over.

title: Tea Timer's Ball
description: The Tea Timers throw a dance and invite everyone in the Creek. Craig believes it's solely to prank him, while Kelsey deals with an unwanted admirer.

title: Tea Timer's Ball
description: The Tea Timers throw a dance and invite everyone in the Creek. Craig believes it's solely to prank him, while Kelsey deals with an unwanted admirer.

title: Bored Games
description: Bored on a rainy day, Craig, Kelsey and JP put together their broken board games and find themselves transported into the ultimate gaming challenge.

title: Ancients of the Creek
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP discover an ancient fort that belonged to the first kids in the Creek.

title: The Champion's Hike
description: Craig joins his former enemies, the Champions of the Other Side of the Creek, on a hike to a secret waterfall.

title: Afterschool Snackdown
description: Craig enters a food competition in the Creek but worries he may be out of his league.

title: Sugar Smugglers
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP become smugglers to sneak candy to kids in need.

title: Lost & Found
description: Craig and his friends visit the Creek's Lost & Found, hoping to claim a puzzle cube.

title: Dodgy Decisions
description: Friends and rivals are pitted against each other in a dangerous game of dodgeball.

title: Opposite Day
description: Opposite Day turns out to be the opposite of what nobody didn't think it wouldn't be.

title: In Search of Lore
description: Craig searches for more clues to aid his quest for the Heart of the Forest.

title: Adventures in Baby Casino
description: Craig goes all in at the Baby Casino.

title: Grandma Smugglers
description: Craig helps Raj sneak his grandmother away to the Creek.

title: Sour Candy Trials
description: Craig goes on a mind-bending journey as he tries to eat the most sour candy in the Creek!

title: Chrono Moss
description: Craig and his friends come upon a mysterious Moss Village, which could aid them in their quest for the Heart of the Forest.

title: Fall Anthology
description: In an attempt to finish a school project, Craig remembers some of his favorite Fall moments.

title: Trick or Creek
description: It's Halloween at the Creek, and Craig is on a mission to collect as much candy as humanly possible, but a spooky ghoul from the Creek's past threatens his haul.

title: The Cardboard Identity
description: Craig and his friends stumble upon a mysterious bunker made of cardboard beneath the Creek.
